::dia(#ch6_1_dia21) sz=13 vw=A1N13 base=none at=1 mv=F7E6N13F6 ab="D6 E5 E7 F6 F8 G7 N13" aw="E6 F4 F5 F7 G8"
Problem 8Black to play

How can Black capture some white stones?

::h3
Answer 8

::dia(#ch6_1_dia22) sz=13 vw=A1N13 base=none at=1 mv=F8 ab="D8 E7 E9 F10 F8 G9" aw="E8 F6 F7 F9 G10"
Correct Answer

By playing 1, Black captures two white stones at the same time.

::dia(#ch6_1_dia23) sz=13 vw=A1N13 base=none at=1 ab="D8 E7 E9 F10 F8 G9" aw="F6 F7 G10"
The Resulting Shape

This is what the position will look like after the capture.

