Correct Answer

Black can capture three stones by playing 1.

::dia(#ch6_1_dia29) sz=13 vw=A1N13 base=none at=1 mv=G7 ab="F5 F6 G4 H4 H6 J5 J6" aw="F7 G5 G6 G7 G8 H5 H7 J4 K4"
If White Plays First

If it’s White’s turn, he can save his three stones by playing 1.

