Answer 11

::dia(#ch6_1_dia31) sz=13 vw=A1N13 base=none at=1 mv=G1 ab="E3 F2 F3 F4 G1 G5 H2 H3 H4" aw="D3 E2 E5 F1 F5 G2 G3 G4"
Correct Answer

Black can capture three stones by playing 1.

::dia(#ch6_1_dia32) sz=13 vw=E1N9 base=none at=1 mv=K5J4K4K3H3J5 ab="H3 J4 K3 K4 K5 L6 M3 M4 M5" aw="H4 J3 J5 J6 K2 K6 L3 L4 L5"
