Answer 12

::dia(#ch6_1_dia34) sz=13 vw=A1N13 base=none at=1 mv=D1 ab="D1 E2 E3 E4 E6 F1" aw="D2 D3 E1 F2 F3 H3"
Correct Answer

Black can capture one stone by playing 1.

